    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small lightweight tiered stands, often folding and portable, intended to be used alongside a table for holding such light foods as muffins.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
